    "profile": "Spanish musical group formed in Pamplona (Navarra) in 1954 and disbanded in 1965 after more than 2500 gigs and more than 200 releases. It was composed in final form by [a5089623], [a5089624] (leader) and [a5089621] (the three vocals and guitar) [a5089622] (accordion) and [a5089620] (voice).\r\nThey has a contract with Belter for 100 recorded songs, half folk, half popular trend.\r\n\r\nSome records of their discography:\r\n1958 - LP en Zafiro: El San Fermín\r\n1959 - LP en Zafiro: Estampas Norteñas\r\n1969 - LP en Zafiro: Aires Norteños\r\n\r\n1958 - EP en Zafiro: Irritzi de Iruña / Oberena / Nosotros los de Iruña / Navarrerias\r\n1959 - EP en Zafiro: Es que le aprieta el calor / La molinera / Al verte, Navarra mia / Yo, lo pongo con orgullo / Una guitarra de plata / Por el color que tenia\r\n1959 - EP en Zafiro: Claveles mios / Un poco mas de su amor / Andele, amigo / Caridad no ta vini\r\n1959 - EP en Zafiro: Estampas Navarras / Aldapa / Joshe Miguel / Los de Cuenca\r\n1959 - EP en Zafiro: Gamberro / Tapate",
